data.enText: a system of communication by telephone or radio inside an office, plane, etc.; the device you press or switch on to start using this system

data.chText: 通过内部通话系统宣布
data.enText: to announce sth over the intercom

data.chText: 他们用内部通话系统呼叫他。
data.enText: They called him on the intercom.

tr: a communication system linking different rooms within a building or ship etc

value.def: An intercom is a small box with a microphone which is connected to a loudspeaker in another room. You use it to talk to the people in the other room.
value.tran: 内部通话系统(或设备);对讲机
